# Privacy Policy — Where Is This Brand From?

Last updated: [06.03.2026]

"Where Is This Brand From?" ("the App") is a logo and brand geography quiz game.

**Data we collect:** We do not collect any personal information. All game
progress (coins, answered companies, streaks) is stored locally on your device
and never transmitted to any server.

**Third-party advertising:** The App uses Google AdMob to display advertisements.
AdMob may collect device identifiers (including the Advertising ID) for the
purpose of serving personalised or non-personalised ads. For more information,
see Google's Privacy Policy at https://policies.google.com/privacy.

**Children:** The App is rated Everyone and contains no content inappropriate
for any age. Ad personalisation follows Google's policies for all age groups.

